{"tid":2066373,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"娜璉狂迷預告下月赴韓","createTime":"2020-06-16T08:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T07:26:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"438e317b056c43c9d6defd1db04073eac0d46fe5","tid":2066373,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"韓國女團TWICE的24歲成員娜璉去年屢遭德國狂迷Josh跟蹤騷擾，Josh日前發文並上載片段，透露網上有很多關於自己的假新聞，但因為受武漢肺炎影響令他無法赴韓，他透露只要入境限制一解除，預計下月初回韓聯繫娜璉。TWICE所屬的JYP事務所表示：「由於此人居住在海外，所以調查難以有所進展。目前已申請人身保護令，禁止他接近娜璉，進入韓國時亦會聯繫出入境管理局，將他繩之於法。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，娜璉前日孖隊友上《人氣歌謠》節目，並為隊友周子瑜慶祝21歲生日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200616/R2DC4U2BDAUWHVBZBZXHTVI56A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200616%2FR2DC4U2BDAUWHVBZBZXHTVI56A%2F&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aaxSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=d7e24f6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200616%2FR2DC4U2BDAUWHVBZBZXHTVI56A%2F&h=b8e22668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200616/R2DC4U2BDAUWHVBZBZXHTVI56A/</a>"},{"pid":"324b4573ef794a5b5fde7295b909f564755db479","tid":2066373,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/g2ygamTnfCbHkNdD4VQf99OTPP0=/802x563/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4R5WTW2GKK42FBSPOTKIUIJFYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fg2ygamTnfCbHkNdD4VQf99OTPP0%3D%2F802x563%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4R5WTW2GKK42FBSPOTKIUIJFYI.jpg&h=ea88d8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n娜璉的德國狂迷Josh聲稱網上有很多自己的假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 